<promed@promedmail.org>

[Denial is the SARS-CoV-2 best friend as it permeates a geographic area in a stealth manner until the "explosive" stage occurs when individuals at high risk of serious disease are infected. It is starting to unfold now in Japan -- a society that has no problems accepting using face masks, but like elsewhere in the world the 20- to 30-year-olds think they are invincible and are forgoing social distancing. A recipe for trouble. - Mod.MPP]

