[B] South Korea: 14 092 confirmed cases, 298 deaths (86 imported, 29 locally transmitted) http://ncov.mohw.go.kr/en/bdBoardList.do?brdId=16&brdGubun=161&dataGubun=&ncvContSeq=&contSeq=&board_id=&gubun=

